## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfcontext/dwarfcontextstate">DWARFContextState</a> This structure contains all member variables for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfcontext">DWARFContext</a> that need to be protected in multi-threaded environments.

Threading support can be enabled by setting the ThreadSafe to true when constructing a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfcontext">DWARFContext</a> to allow DWARRContext to be able to be used in a multi-threaded environment, or not enabled to allow for maximum performance in single threaded environments.
